White House fan Ron Wade has built an exact replica of the Oval Office in his home costing more than $200,000.

The father-of-two painstakingly recreated the White House's most famous room over four years. 

Obsessed Mr Wade also owns the world's largest collection of presidential memorabilia which is squeezed into the family home.

